\id 2TI - Nchane
\h 2 Timoti
\toc1 Ŋwa wù kiŋgane kifɛɛ wu Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ Timoti le
\toc2 2 Timoti
\toc3 2Ti
\mt2 Ŋwa wù kiŋgane kifɛɛ wù Bol gɛ̀ saŋ fɛ
\mt1 Timoti
\mt2 le
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì le a Ŋwa wu Timoti wù kiŋgane kinfɛɛ wunɛ le
\ip A ŋwa wunɛ le baaŋ, le nyume nteefɛ yì Bol nya Timoti le njɛ muh wù bɛ wu lɛne wu fiih wu. Wu jɛme baaŋ kune shɛ́ŋ yì kanɛ. Wu teefe Timoti no wu gɛ̂ɛne fwe bɛ lɛme che chì wu lɛne fɛ Jiso Kletu le bɛ fitele fimimia, bɛ no wu jîjɛ n'yɛyɛ wù kooji wù le wu saaka wù joŋe bɛ wu maŋkaŋ mà kege. Wu teede tɛ no wu lé wu gêe lɛme che njɛ muh wu n'yɛyɛ bɛ muh wù jiɛnyi wu feeji jɛ yi Nyo chuule mo no wu yɛnɛ baŋgɛ nɛɛ, kɛnɛ bamii tɛɛnyi bɛ wu nɛɛ.
\ip Bol le wu jɛmɛ Timoti le chuule lɛ wu yɛ̂ne keefɛ wu jâ wu lêesɛ kibo fɛ bambejɛ ba kiyuŋ bɛ ba achiji le gɛ (2:23). Yi mwɛɛ munɛ le munchii le wu tane Timoti lɛ wu jô mbejɛ yi nche we le.
\iot Bikwɛɛ bi mwɛɛ mù le a Ŋwa wunɛ le
\io1 1:1-2 Fɛŋkɛɛ
\io1 1:3–2:13 Bol nya kiyone Nyo le kune Timoti wu ka yufe fitele fie
\io1 2:14–4:5 Bol teefɛ Timoti
\io1 4:6-18 Bol jɛmɛ kune kikwɛɛ ke
\io1 4:19-22 Kimɛsɛ
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Le mɛ wù Bol, nle mwa ntuŋ wu Kletu Jiso yi ŋkoŋ wu Nyo le. Fi finɛ bii ŋka wù kune kinche kì kage gɛ kì le yi Kletu Jiso le.
\p 
\v 2 Nsaŋe ŋwa wunɛ fɛ wo le Timoti mwa yaŋ. Wo le fitele fiaŋ.
\p Nyo wù Chii bɛ Kletu Jiso wu Tada wese besabɛŋ bo dunyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ wo le, bo koo yii fɛ wo le, bo nya wo bɛ nyiɛgee.
\s1 Bol nya kiyone Nyo le kune Timoti wu ka wu yufɛ fitele fie
\p 
\v 3 Segechii nto ŋkwaji wo antaŋ bɛ fɛnshe a buunɛ chaŋ le nyaa gɛh nyu kiyone Nyo wù nlɛne wu le, fiɛɛ sage gɛ mɛ fɛ fitele le gɛ, gɛh no bachii gɛ̀ lɛne.
\v 4 Nto ŋkwaji tɛ ajoo a wo gɛ̀ shiishi sege besa wo gɛ̀ gase, jɛŋ tu yi yuu mɛ antaŋ bɛ fɛnshe lɛ mbee n'yɛŋ wo le, wu lɛ fitele fiaŋ yisɛ bɛ njoŋ.
\v 5 Nto ŋkwaji tɛ mbɛmɛ wo wù nchiɛɛŋ wù wo kɛme. Mbɛmɛ wunɛ gɛ̀ ya kɛme bwee bwoo wù Loy bɛ bwoo wù Yuni, ŋkee lo gɛ mɛ maŋe gɛ, lɛ le wu wù wo kɛme mɛɛse.
\v 6 Le fiɛɛ fì ŋgoone ki ntâne wo lɛ wo kâasɛ wo kâŋsɛ yi nya yi Nyo yì le ye yo le, wo fîee njɛ ŋgu. Nnya yinɛ le yì wo gɛ̀ kɛmɛ sege ŋgɛ̀ ŋgɛlɛ chiaaŋ yaŋ yi wo le.
\v 7 Ŋkee lɛ Nyo gɛ̀ baaŋ nya gɛ kiyo besabɛŋ le lɛ ki gêe besabɛŋ kɛme nfaaŋ gɛ. Wu gɛ̀ nya nyume kiyo ki bvuŋga bɛ ki kiŋkoŋɛ mo kì taŋlo ki gê lɛ besabɛŋ kêe ki bee shêe bɛ bikwɛɛ biɛsa besabɛŋ.
\p 
\v 8 Noo, keefɛ wo kɛ̂me bvuya ki wo jɛ̂me bamii bamu le kune Tada wese besabɛŋ kɛnɛ kune mɛ wù nlɛne ncha nje wu gɛ. Geenɛ wo jôde tɛ wo ŋgɛ yi saaka wù joŋe wunɛ le bɛ bvuŋga bvù Nyo nya wo le.
\v 9 Le Nyo wu gɛ̀ bvusɛ besabɛŋ, wu tɛɛŋ besabɛŋ lɛ besabɛŋ chêe kinche ki bamii ba le be. Gɛ wu gɛ̀ ge finɛ fiɛɛ nyume nje lɛme chimi chì besabɛŋ gɛ̀ ge gɛ. Gɛ̀ bee nje nseesɛ we fɛ besabɛŋ le, bɛ fitele fì joŋe fì wu gɛ̀ kɛme fɛ besabɛŋ le fede yi Kletu Jiso le, baaŋ lo fɛ woŋ kɛ.
\v 10 Mɛɛse Nyo le wu dunyɛ wa fitele fì joŋe fiyu fɛ besabɛŋ le no Mbvusɛ wese besabɛŋ wù Kletu Jiso le wu to wa. Wu le wu ŋgodɛ bvuŋga bvu kwe, wu dunyɛ kinche waaŋ, lɛ gɛ muh baaŋ wu ka wu kwe gɛ. Wu le wu ge fi bu andaŋandaŋ bɛ saaka wù joŋe.
\v 11 Le saaka wù joŋe wuyu wunɛ wù Nyo le wu baa mɛ lɛ nyûme muh wu nfejɛ bɛ mwa ntuŋ wu Kletu mo muh wu n'yɛyɛ wuyu.
\v 12 Le nje finɛ fi n'yɛne ŋgɛ wù n'yɛne wunɛ nɛ. Geenɛ gɛ ŋkɛme bvuya gɛ, nje ŋkee muh wù nlese fitele yi ye ye le. Ŋkee lo, kimaŋɛ sɛŋ lɛ wu taŋlo wu jîiŋe fɛ fiɛɛ fì nle nya chiaaŋ ye le finɛ\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Kɛnɛ lɛ, “Wu taŋlo wu jiiŋe fɛ fiɛɛ fì wu le wu nya chiaaŋ yaŋ le finɛ”,\f* gɛɛŋ bu juu chì kimɛsɛ.
\v 13 Wo bîi gɛh bwɛŋ wu n'yɛyɛ wù kooji wù ŋgɛ̀ n'yɛyɛ wo yu. No wo bii yu noo wo lêese gɛh fitele nyume yi Kletu le, wo kɛ̂me tɛ kiŋkoŋɛ fɛ bamii le, fichii nyûme a je yi bamii ba le ba Kletu Jiso le.
\v 14 Wo jîiŋe n'yɛyɛ wù nchiɛɛŋ wù ba gɛ̀ nya chiaaŋ yo le. Wo jîiŋe bɛ bvuŋga bvu Kiyo ki Yuude ki le ye yese besabɛŋ le.
\p 
\v 15 Wo kee lo lɛ bamii bachii ba kimbe kì Ɛsia le gɛ̀ noŋ wa mɛ. Ŋgoo yiboo le Figelu bɛ Hɛmogene.
\v 16 Nlɛge lɛ Tada kôo yii fɛ yeh yi Onesifolu le. Wu to wu gee chikɛ le chikɛ le shɛ́ŋ yaŋ jiɛɛ. Wu gɛ̀ baaŋ kɛmɛ gɛ bvuya nje ncha wu nle wu le gɛ.
\v 17 Sege wu gɛ̀ fɛsɛ Lum yanɛ, wu gɛ̀ bosɛ shɛ́ŋ ki wu gôoŋ mɛ, gɛ̂ɛŋ bu fɛ wu yɛ̂ŋ mɛne.
\v 18 Mbuune lɛ Tada ge doo nyume juu chi kimɛsɛ, Tada kôo yii fɛ wu le. Wo kee lo chuule lɛme chichii chì wu gɛ̀ lɛŋ fɛ mɛne a kilaantɛŋ kì Ɛfɛsu le.
\c 2
\s1 No taŋlo Timoti jûu yi fiɛɛ fì Nyo le
\p 
\v 1 Timoti mwa yaŋ, ndoo ntu fɛ wo le, wo lɛ̂me gɛh wo tɛɛme bii fitele fì joŋe fì Kletu Jiso dunyɛ fɛ bamii ba taashɛ bɛ wu le.
\v 2 Wo jôde fiɛɛ fì wo to wo yuge njɛme a bamii fwe wesee wo lêese chiaaŋ yi bamii ba chaaŋ le bo nyu bo kojɛ ki taŋlo bo yɛ̂yi bamii bamu yu.
\v 3 Wo jôde tɛ wo ŋgɛ njɛ muh jɛŋ wù kooji wu Kletu Jiso.
\v 4 Sege muh wu jɛŋ le yi lɛme che le gɛ wu ka leese kikwɛɛ fɛ mwɛɛ mu bamii ba le gɛ bamii ba jɛŋ le gɛ, nje fiɛɛ fì wu jiiŋe yi fi le, le ki wù gêe fiɛɛ fì chiji kikwɛɛ ke goone.
\v 5 Le gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no gɛ muh wù lege kinlegɛ taŋlo wu legɛ wu so fiɛɛ, njɛ wu lege wu bii banchi ba kinlegɛ le sɛŋ gɛ.
\v 6 Muh wu mwɛ wù lɛne tɛ chuule le wu kɛ̂me ki wu yâ wu môŋ fiɛɛ antɛnɛɛ a mwɛɛ mù wu gɛ̀ bonɛ.
\v 7 Wo kwâji kune mwɛɛ mù njɛme munɛ Tada lé wu gê wo kɛ̂ɛ mu munchii.
\p 
\v 8 Wo kwâji kune Jiso Kletu wù gɛ̀ bu yi kwe le. Wu gɛ̀ bee muh wu a kfuu chi Nfoŋ Dabi le. Le fi fì nfeeji a saaka waŋ wù joŋe le.
\v 9 Le nje saaka wù joŋe wunɛ wù n'yɛne ŋgɛ yu, mɛ nyume yi bancha le njɛ muh wù ŋgode nchi. Geenɛ, mo no nle yi bancha le noo, gɛ jɛ yi Nyo nyume yi bancha le gɛ.
\v 10 No fi le noo, mɛ mo ntu ŋkaane shɛ́ŋ yi fiɛɛ le fichii nje bamii ba Nyo le wu cha, wu lɛ bo tɛ ge bo kɛ̂mɛ mbvusɛ fede yi Kletu Jiso le bɛ bvukugɛ bvù kage gɛ.
\v 11 Njɛmɛ wunɛ le nchiɛɛŋ, wù le lɛ:
\q1 Nɛ besabɛŋ le be taashɛ be kwe besa wu,
\q1 besabɛŋ chêe tɛ besa wu.
\q1 
\v 12 Nɛ besabɛŋ kaane shɛ́ŋ,
\q1 besabɛŋ tô be sâge bvunfoŋ besa wu.
\q1 Nɛ besabɛŋ faŋ lo wu,
\q1 wu to wu faŋ tɛ besabɛŋ.
\q1 
\v 13 Nɛ besabɛŋ le njɛ bee lɛme be tɛɛme sɛŋ,
\q1 wu mɛ gɛh wu lɛme wu tɛɛme,
\q1 nje gɛ taŋlo wu faŋ kikwɛɛ ke gɛ.
\s1 Muh wu lɛme wù Nyo le wu bɛɛŋ
\p 
\v 14 Wo ntâne bo bɛ mwɛɛ munɛ, wo ka wo jɛme a Nyo fwe lɛ bo lû bɛ kintɛɛnyɛ ki jɛ́. Gɛ mu fii muh gɛ. Mu chɛŋe gɛh lo bɛ bamii ba yege mu le.
\v 15 Wo mône chuule ki wo dûunyi kikwɛɛ kuŋ a Nyo jii njɛ muh wù Nyo yɛne lɛ le wù kooji. Wo nyûme muh wu lɛme wù kɛme gɛ fiɛɛ fì bvuya kôode wu yi fi le gɛ, bɛ wu jiji kinchiɛɛŋ ki jɛ yi Nyo le a je yì kooji le.
\v 16 Wo wɛ̂ɛne lo bɛ banjɛmɛ ba kɛme gɛ fiɛɛ ki bo ge bɛ Nyo gɛ, nje banjɛmɛ bayu le bo ge bamii chêe nyume kinche kì Nyo goone gɛ bo gɛɛne yu fwe.
\v 17 Ban'yɛyɛ baboo bayu jade bo nyume njɛ nfu wù jii ye yi muh wu yaade wu gɛɛne. Ŋgoo yi bamii ba yɛyi n'yɛyɛ wuyu wunɛ le Amenayu bɛ Filitu.
\v 18 Bo le bo chinɛ wa je yì nchiɛɛŋ le no bo lɛme lɛ mbu wu yi kwe le, le wu jo wa kijusɛ. Bo doo bo gee noo, bo chɛŋe bɛ mbɛmɛ wu bamii bamu.
\v 19 Geenɛ, kichi kì lese Nyo le ki tɛɛme, ki lɛme gɛh fo. Kichi kinɛ Nyo le wu saŋ njiŋɛ yu we lɛ, “Tada kee bamii ba le be”, bɛ lɛ, “Muh wuchii wù bɛɛne jee chi Tada, wu kɛme ki wu chînɛ gee chì befe le.”
\p 
\v 20 Mwɛɛ mu yeh yi muh wù baaŋ le gɛ to nyume gɛh shú bɛ ŋkáa mo muŋkoo mù ba kɛnyi bɛ kichwa ki bige kì yɛɛde kɛnɛ kì baaŋ gɛ. Mumu to mu nyume tɛ mù ba kɛnyi bɛ bite mo mù ba kɛnyi bɛ nshɛŋ yì chimɛ. Mwɛɛ munɛ mumu to mu nyume mù kɛme lɛme chì kuge, mumu nyume mù kɛme gɛh lo lɛme chì nchɛ.
\v 21 Noo, muh nɛ le wu bvusɛ chiaaŋ ye fɛ mwɛɛ mù achiji le, tu wu le wa njɛ fiɛɛ fi yeh fì taŋlo ba jo ba gee lɛme chì kuge yu. Wu le muh wù Nyo le wu ge lɛ wu nyume muh we. Wu le wa muh wù chiɛɛne lo chiji kikwɛɛ ke lɛ wu jôde wu gêe lɛme che chì joŋe mo chì la yu.
\v 22 Noo, wo lêgɛ lo fiuŋ mwɛɛ mù fɛde ye yufe kiŋghaŋ. Wo mône fiuŋ ki wo chêe kinche nyume kì chaaŋ bɛ ki wo kɛ̂me mbɛmɛ mo kiŋkoŋɛ bɛ kinche kì nyiɛgee. Wo gêe noo gɛh no bamii ba tɛŋe tɛ jee chi Tada bɛ muntele muboo mu yuude gee.
\v 23 Keefɛ wo kɛ̂me lo fiɛɛ ki wo gê bɛ bambejɛ ba kiyuŋ bɛ ba achiji gɛ, nje bo to bo too gɛh nyu bɛ waa.
\v 24 Gɛ muh wù lɛme wu Tada kɛme ki wu wâade bɛ bamii gɛ. Wu kɛme ki wu kɛ̂me gɛh nyu fitele fì joŋe fɛ muh le wuchii, wu nyume muh wù kee ki wu yɛ̂yi bamii, wu kee tɛ ki wu kâane shɛ́ŋ bɛ bamii.
\v 25 Wu to wu naji fiɛɛ nyiɛgee bɛ bamii ba tɛɛnyi bɛ wu. Wu to wu naji noo bɛ ŋkwajɛ lɛ taŋlo Nyo fî bo, bo kûsɛ muntele muboo bo kɛɛ fiɛɛ fì nchiɛɛŋ,
\v 26 bo mo bo tɛ̂ɛŋ bvufee bvuboo jiŋ, bo lêgɛ bo bû a kintase ki debele kì wu le wu koo bo yo lɛ bo gêe gɛh nyume fiɛɛ fì wu koŋe.
\c 3
\s1 Mwɛɛ mù kuufe ye lé mu gê mu kôoshi aju a fɛkimɛsɛ le
\p 
\v 1 Wo kêe lɛ, lé tô nyûme aju a kimɛsɛ le, mwɛɛ mù tɛɛme lé mu kôoshi wesee.
\v 2 Bamii lé bo jâ bo kôŋe wa nyume bikwɛɛ biboo, bo koŋe bige, bo chiaase ye, bo ŋage, bo jɛme jɛ́ yì befe kune bamii bamu. Gɛ bo baaŋ bo yûge babwee baboo le bɛ bachiji baboo le gɛ, gɛ bo nyu bo nyâa lo kiyone yi fiɛɛ le gɛ, gɛ bo nyu bo kɛ̂me gee chì yuude gɛ.
\v 3 Gɛ bo nyu bo kɛ̂me yii fɛ bamii le gɛ, gɛ bo nyu bo lɛ̂ɛshi tɛ bajialɛ ba bamii lɛ gɛ. Bo chɛŋe bɛ ajee a bamii, bo jiji gɛ ye yiboo le gɛ. Bo kɛme nyu gee chì kuufe ye, bo koŋe gɛ fiɛɛ fì joŋe gɛ.
\v 4 Bo lé bo kâde munaŋ bamii le, bo chee kinche kì nchɛ nchɛ, bo yisɛ bɛ kinchiaasɛ ye. Bo lé bo kôŋe ki bo jii gɛh nyume bikwɛɛ biboo fede ki bo koŋe Nyo.
\v 5 Bo lé bo dûunyi lɛ bo lɛme yi fiɛɛ fi Nyo le, geenɛ bo ka faŋe bvuŋga bvu fiɛɛ fi Nyo fiyu. Wo lêge lo kfuu chi bobaa bamii.
\v 6 Bamii banɛ bamu jiɛnyi bo lese yéh yi bamii le bo shiide a we a bikɛse ba wɛɛyi, ba bimbefɛ biboo nyu bi yigɛ wa bo, bo tu bo njiine bo bii nyume kiŋkoŋɛ ki mwɛɛ le yeye yeye.
\v 7 Bo banɛ bikɛse le ba to bo she bo yege n'yɛyɛ segechii, geenɛ taŋlo bo gɛ yu bo kɛɛ fiɛɛ fì le nchiɛɛŋ gɛ.
\v 8 No Jani bɛ Jamblɛ gɛ̀ tɛɛnyi bɛ Musɛ, le gɛh yɛɛŋyɛɛŋ no bamii banɛ tɛɛnyi nchiɛɛŋ wu Nyo. Le bamii ba bvufee bvuboo le bvu fiisɛ wa, fitele fì bo jɛme lɛ bo le bo leesɛ yi Kletu le nyu chimbiaŋ.
\v 9 Geenɛ gɛ bo nyume bo ge noo gɛɛŋ bu je yì ndefe le gɛ, nje kiyuŋ kiboo lé ki bû tɛ ki chûnyɛ waaŋ fɛ bamii le bachii, gɛh no ki Jani bɛ Jamblɛ gɛ̀ bu.
\s1 Bol teefɛ Timoti lɛ wu lɛ̂me gɛh yi fiɛɛ fì bo yɛyi wu yu le
\p 
\v 10 Timoti, wo le fiuŋ wo kee wa kune n'yɛyɛ waŋ bɛ kinche kaŋ mo fiɛɛ fì ŋgoone. Wo kee tɛ kune fitele fì nlese yi Nyo le bɛ shɛ́ŋ yì nto ŋkaane, mo kiŋkoŋɛ kì ŋkɛme fɛ bamii le, bɛ no nto mone yi fiɛɛ le fichii ŋgɛɛne fwe.
\v 11 Wo kee tɛ bikaa bì bamii gɛ̀ boone a mɛ jiŋ mo baŋgɛ baŋ. Wo kee mwɛɛ mù gɛ̀ kooshɛ bɛ mɛ Antiok bɛ Ikoniuŋ mo Lista. Wo kee kfuu chi bikaa bì bamii gɛ̀ boone a mɛ jiŋ. Geenɛ yi baŋgɛ banɛ le bachii Tada gɛ̀ fi mɛ.
\v 12 Fi le nchiɛɛŋ lɛ muh wuchii wù goone ki wu chêe kinche ki Nyo goone njɛ muh wu le wù taashɛ wa bɛ Kletu Jiso le ba nyume ba bôone bikaa a wu jiŋ.
\v 13 Bamii ba ghɛge mwɛɛ bɛ bamii ba lɛɛde bamu, gee chiboo le chi foo chi gɛɛne lo, no bo lɛɛde bɛ bamii bamu bo lɛɛde tɛ bɛ bikwɛɛ biboo.
\v 14 Geenɛ, fɛ wo le, wo lɛ̂me gɛh nyu yi fiɛɛ fì ba le ba yɛyɛ wo yu, wo bɛɛŋ bɛ fitele fiuŋ fichii. Wo lɛ̂me yi fi le nje wo kee bamii ba gɛ̀ yɛyɛ wo yu.
\v 15 Wo gɛ̀ kɛ wo kee mwɛɛ mù ba saŋ a Ŋwa wu Nyo le wo baaŋ mwa wù shige. Mwɛɛ munɛ taŋlo mu têefɛ wo, wo tô wo kɛ̂mɛ mbvusɛ yi fitele fì wo leese yi Kletu Jiso le.
\v 16 Fiɛɛ fichii fì ba saŋ a Ŋwa wu Nyo le, le bvufee bvuyu ja fɛ Nyo le. Fi fii ki fi yɛ̂yɛ bamii, fi chûunyi bajialɛ, fi nâji bamii, fi yɛyi bamii bɛ kinche kì chaaŋ,
\v 17 wu lɛ muh wù le muh wu Nyo nyûme muh wù kojɛ, wù kɛme fiɛɛ fichii ki wu gêe lɛme chì joŋe yu chichii.
\c 4
\s1 Bol teefɛ Timoti lɛ wu gêe lɛme che chuule
\p 
\v 1 Njɛme finɛ wo le, a Nyo fwe bɛ Kletu Jiso wu lé wu sâ bamii ba baaŋ yu bɛ ba kweeyɛ wa. Njɛme nɛ nje mbunɛ we wù wu lé wu yû wu tô wu bûnɛ mo bvunfoŋ bwe njɛme lɛ,
\v 2 wo fêeji jɛ yi Nyo. Wo fêeji gɛh wo gɛɛne yu fwe, kɛnɛ nyume kife ki kojɛ le kɛnɛ ki baaŋ kojɛ gɛ le. Wo dûunyi bajialɛ ba bamii lɛ, wo naji bo, wo yufe muntele muboo bɛ nyiɛgee no n'yɛyɛ wo le.
\v 3 Wo kêe lɛ kife too lo ki bamii baaŋ gɛ bo lɛ̂me yi n'yɛyɛ wù kooji le gɛ. Bintuŋ biboo lé bi gê bi fûu ki bi yûge wa nyu fiɛɛ fimi yeye. Bo mo bo gôoŋ bamii ba n'yɛyɛ, bo le bo le, ba le bo yɛ̂yi wa nyu fiɛɛ fì bo koŋe ki bo yûge.
\v 4 Bo lé bo chînɛ ki bo yûge nyume fiɛɛ fì nchiɛɛŋ le, bo shɛ̂ŋe bo gɛ̂ɛne gɛh nyume a mumaŋa mu achiji le.
\v 5 Geenɛ, fɛ wo le, wo lêese kikwɛɛ kuŋ chaaŋ segechii, wo kâane shɛ́ŋ yi baŋgɛ le, wo gêe lɛme chi muh wu jiɛnyi lo wu feeji jɛ yi Nyo. Wo gêe lɛme chuŋ chichii chi ba le ba nya chiaaŋ yo le.
\p 
\v 6 Fɛ mɛne, nle wa mɛɛse njɛ mbvuuŋ, kife kojɛ ka ki ba lé ba jô mɛ ba gê njɛ no ba to ba jo mbvuuŋ ba fu. Kife ki nle ŋkwɛɛ le ki kojɛ ka.
\v 7 Nle n'ju wa bvuju bvu joŋe yi fiɛɛ fì Nyo le, nlege kinlegɛ mɛsɛ, njijɛ mbɛmɛ waŋ le mɛ gɛh yu.
\v 8 Kɛge yi mɛɛse le ba gɛɛ wa kifo kaŋ ki bvunfoŋ ki le ki kinche kì chaaŋ. Kifo kinɛ le ki Tada wu le muh wù sage bansa chaaŋ, le wu wù lé wu bôoŋ ki a mɛ fwa yi juu chi kimɛsɛ le. Gɛ wu nyume wu booŋ gɛh nyume kaŋ maa gɛ. Wu lé wu bôoŋ tɛ bi bamii bachii ba chiɛɛne bo koŋe lɛ wu kâasɛ wu tô.
\s1 Bol sɛɛŋ no mwɛɛ le a kimbe ke le
\p 
\v 9 Timoti, môoŋ chuule ki wo yâŋsɛ wo tô chige fɛ mɛne.
\v 10 Wo kêe lɛ Dɛma le wu koŋ wa woŋ wu mɛɛse kfunɛ, wu noŋ mɛ wù gɛɛŋ Tɛsalonika. Klesɛŋ le wu gɛɛŋ Galɛshiaŋ, Taytu gɛɛŋ Dalmatia.
\v 11 Mɛ gɛh Luka wu maa wu le besa wu. Sege wo too, wo jo Maliku bena wu too. Taŋlo wu fîi mɛ baaŋ yi lɛme le.
\v 12 Tichiku, nle ntuŋ wu Ɛfɛsu.
\v 13 Sege wo too, wo jo kikuŋ kaŋ kì baaŋ ki ŋgɛ ŋgɛlɛ a Kabu yeh a kilaantɛŋ ki Towa le. Wo tôo tɛ bɛ baŋwa baŋ, fede munchii mu ba fɛ bɛ je yi nyaŋ.
\p 
\v 14 Alɛksanda wu suŋe kilamɛ le wu ge ŋgɛ bɛ mɛ, nyume gɛ wu wɛɛ gɛ. Tada lé wu lâŋɛ wu yi gee che le.
\v 15 Wo yɛ̂ne tɛ bena wu. Wu tɛɛnyi baaŋ kune saaka wu besabɛŋ feeji wunɛ le.
\p 
\v 16 Yi juu chi fwe le yi nsa waŋ le, chi ŋgɛ nto nlɛɛŋ yi tɛdɛ chi nsa le, muh gɛ̀ baaŋ lɛɛŋ gɛ a mɛ jiŋ gɛ. Bamii bachii gɛ̀ bee bo legɛ lo mɛ. Keefɛ Nyo sâ bo yi fi fiɛɛ le gɛ.
\v 17 Geenɛ, Tada gɛ̀ lɛɛŋ a mɛ jiŋ, wu nya mɛ bɛ bvuŋga ki nfejɛ saaka wù joŋe chuule wu lɛ bamii bachii ba le gɛ Bajuu gɛ yu saaka wuyu. Noo, wu gɛ̀ be wu bvusɛ mɛ jwe wu bvule le.
\v 18 Tada lé wu bvûuse gɛh mɛ chiaaŋ yi fiɛɛ fì befe le fichii, wu lé wu yû wu tô wu lêesɛ mɛ bvunfoŋ bwe bvu fɛwe le yi nyiɛŋgee le. Besabɛŋ bɛ̂ɛŋse wu segechii bee luu gɛ. Fi nyûme noo.
\s1 Ban'yɛsɛ
\p 
\v 19 Yɛ̂sɛ Blisila bɛ Akwela le wo nya mɛne. Wo yɛ̂sɛ tɛ yeh yi Onesifolu le.
\v 20 Ɛlastu gɛ̀ shɛɛ Kolɛŋ, Tofimu le ŋgɛ nchinɛ wu le Miletu wu chɛne.
\v 21 Wo moŋ chuule ki wo tô fɛ nfuŋ wu tɛɛme ge wu kɛ. Yubulu chiiŋse n'yɛsɛ wo le. Budeŋ bɛ Lɛnu mo Klawdia bɛ booŋ ba bwee wese besabɛŋ bachii yi Kletu le chiiŋse tɛ n'yɛsɛ.
\v 22 Nlɛge lɛ Tada nyûme bɛ kiyo kuŋ. Wu dûnyɛ fitele fì joŋe fɛ bɛŋ le bachii.
